n,k
(n,k\ge 5)
A
(n+2^k)^{2^k}\equiv  0(\mod 2^{k+1})
(n+2^k)^{2^k}=\sum_{j=0}^{2^k}\binom{2^k}{j}n^{2^k-j}(2^k)^{j}=n^{2^k}+2^k\cdot n^{2^k-1}\cdot 2^k+\cdots=n^{2^k}+2^{k+1}A
2^{k+1}\nmid n^{2^k}
n^n+47\equiv0\pmod{2^l}
n^n+47\not\equiv0\pmod{2^{l+1}}
(n+2^l)^{n+2^l}\equiv(n+2^l)^n \pmod{2^{l+1}}
n
(n+2^l)^{2^l}\equiv 0
(n+2^l)^{n+2^l} \equiv 0
(n+2^l)^{n+2^l} \equiv (n+2^l)^n
(n+2^k)^{2^k}\equiv 1 \pmod {2^{k+1}}
n^{2^k}\equiv 1
(n,2^{k+1})=1
n^{\varphi(2^{k+1})}=n^{2^k}\equiv 1\pmod {2^{k+1}}
